Package: ClimateMosaic
Type: Package
Title: US Climate Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Flavia Jiang [aut, cre], Jasmine Wang [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Flavia Jiang <yj472@cornell.edu>, Jasmine Wang <xw495@cornell.edu>
Description: Functions to analyze climate patterns at weather stations, and make
      and/or visualize interpolations for the contiguous U.S. It is called 
      ClimateMosaic because the interpolation plots look like mosaic.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
